  • Classes
    Class
    Description
    BASIC
    The BASIC class represents a simplified booking application that will have an arraylist of properties and arraylist of users.
    Booking
    Booking class which is used to maintain the bookings in User.
    Host
    The host class will own the property, and will be recorded everytime we create a new property.
    PopulateData
    PopulateData class which will have a static method to populate 3 objects of each class for the program to start working.
    Property
    Property class that will hold properties in the BASIC class according to the UML diagram.
    User
    A User class that we can make use of it in the BASIC class it will have booking arraylist because each user can have multiple booking.
